<dl id="n12126i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12126i">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12126i"> 126(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> a downright little / celebrity</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Vincent Ferrier gagna donc son nouveau poste de L&eacute;rida, modeste et gentille petite ville au beau milieu de la Calalogne <font color="green">[sic]</font>. Il y fut un professeur merveilleux et acquit &agrave; la ronde une v&eacute;ritable petite c&eacute;l&eacute;brit&eacute;. <br><font color="green">[Vincent then reached his new post in Lerida, modest and nice little city right in the centre of Catalogne. There he was a wonderful teacher and acquired all around <mark>a right little celebrity</mark>.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 15</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
